      "comment": "SUPER SPECIAL (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Abraxos (30.18) in a Grade 5/6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Top prospect. FEDERAL SAKI (5) produced a speedy 23.78 winning over 407m at this track last start in a Grade 4/5. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. TRIPPER ART (4) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.12) in a Grade 5 at Capalaba. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Has ability and can measure up. ROCKY RACCOON (2) ran good time (29.99) when second last start over 510m at this track, the second placing in a row.",
